1.title: Wakuwaku! Tama street de dai race/Dokidoki! Lovelin wa dare nihohoemu?
1.plot: Everyone is excited for the Great Race down Tama Street, especially since the big TV star, Lovelin, will be hosting it.

2.title: Kyun! Tamagotchi School no tenkôsei/Doko doko? Lovelitchi no ôchi
2.plot: A new student, a beautiful girl named Lovelitchi, is coming to Tamagotchi School, and everyone is excited. Memetchi forgets to return an accessory of Lovelitchi's, so Mametchi creates a device to track her down.

3.title: Gô gô! TAMAX-TV Kengaku/Kurakura! Ikinari namahôsô
3.plot: Lovelin falls ill during a class field trip, and the students must host her TV shows in her place.

4.title: Shinken! Rainbow soritchi sakusen/Harahara! Lovelin concert
4.plot: Mametchi creates a "Rainbowsoritchi" to cross a river, but the first run doesn't go as planned. Lovelitchi is invited to her own concert by her friends, and must find a way to both perform and be an audience in order to keep her secret.

5.title: Waiwai! Tama tomo dai chôsa/Lovelyn dai tsuiseki! Dawasa
5.plot: Mametchi and his friends decide to do their class project on "Tama Tomos", which sparks a bad memory for Lovelitchi. Uwasatchi tries to find out Lovelitchi's secret, while Lovelitchi performs live with Gotchiman as Lovelin.

6.title: Hi-mi-tsu! Mametchi no tanjôbi/Ki-me-ta! Lovelyn no kokuhaku
6.plot: Mametchi's friend's behavior makes him think that they're mad at him, but they're just planning his surprise birthday party. Lovelitchi offers to have it at her house, but is called to Tamax-TV the day of the party.

7.title: Eê! MameChamametchi/Pachiri! Hachamecha satsuei kai
7.plot: Mametchi is asked to deliver his dad some lunch and brings along his sister Chamametchi, but she gets herself merged with Mametchi by accident. While waiting to have their photo taken by Lovelitchi's father, Memetchi, Makiko, and Flowertchi have fun trying on all of Lovelitchi's costumes and clothes.
